Author: Tettix
Title: [ANN] [ICO launched!!] [TIX] Tettix: Your trade your game!!
Body: https://i.imgur.com/OFyhHiu.jpg  Tettix Official Links WEBSITE | WHITE PAPER | BLOG | TWITTER  Tettix is an Ethereum-based decentralized exchange and lets anyone use their own private wallet provided by MetaMask to trade.   ICO Launched Info.!!!! ICO Bonus : Start Bonus 20% first 5 days ICO end   : 2017/09/21 2017 12:00 UTC ICO contract address : 0xd77fc35cc9007557dcd18bfe26fe66f1ea3a0e7f Token Sale Howto : How to participate in Tettix Token Sale  Tettix Demo Video!! https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bzvAiXYUdXM   Problems with Traditional Exchange Users cannot keep their private key of wallet generated from exchanges; Transaction is not transparent. Users don't know the financial trail; Traditional exchanges hold most part of money, so they can control the market price; Traditional exchanges cannot add new ethereum-based ICO token into their system immediately.  Some references: Russian Held Over Bitcoin Laundering Linked to BTC-E Exchange: Sources Poloniex Loses 12.3% of its Bitcoins in Latest Bitcoin Exchange Hack The Bitfinex Bitcoin Hack: What We Know (And Don't Know)  Why Tettix? The existing exchanges don’t guarantee wallets’ usability. Once exchange closes down, your wallet will become invalid as well. However, Tettix takes Metamask as wallet, which means you can keep your wallet’s private key and no need to worry about its usability.  Our Vision Tettix is creating a REAL decentralized exchange. Our goal is to remove redundant constraints on digital currency transaction. In the short-term, we aim for providing a reliable and convenient ethereum-based trading system. In the long-term, we hope that Tettix can replace all existing centralized exchanges and give everyone a whole new trading experience.  About TIX token For now, TIX is Tettix's internal token. It is used as trading fee when users trade on Tettix and also can be a trading token.  Tettix Crowdfund ICO start: 2017/08/30 2017 12:00 UTC ICO end: 2017/09/21 2017 12:00 UTC  TIX for distribution: 400,000,000 (400,000 ETH)  Token Exchange rate: 10,000 TIX : 1 ETH Currency accepted: ETH ONLY  Start Bonus 20% first 5 days  Minimum transaction amount: 100 TIX (0.01 ETH) Maximum transaction amount: 30,000,000 TIX (3000 ETH)  Tettix Roadmap http://i.imgur.com/bDbtfyJ.png  Blog Index Introduction to Tettix - https://medium.com/@TettixDev/introduction-to-tettix-ae1dc5638749 Details of Tettix - https://medium.com/@TettixDev/details-of-tettix-e5c9f310fa41 Why do we need a decentralized exchange? - https://medium.com/@TettixDev/why-do-we-need-a-decentralized-exchange-7ca9cbc3122e How to participate in Tettix Token Sale  - https://medium.com/@TettixDev/how-to-participate-in-tettix-token-sale-tutorial-dff6c5a98eb3 [Speaker deck] Tettix team presented the Tettix ICO detailed in Blockchain Asia 2017 Workshop  - https://speakerdeck.com/tettixdev/tettix-decentralized-ethereum-token-exchange-platform Tettix Demo Video - How Tettix Operates  - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bzvAiXYUdXM]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bzvAiXYUdXM
